		<br>
		Pavement rehabilition is in progress near Corsicana. I was driving on fresh new concrete when I took this photo.
		Reconstruction has been in progress from Dallas to south of Corsicana since the late 1980s. From Corsicana
		to Dallas, the freeway now has 6 main lanes (except for one section still under construction - see the next photo).
		
		<P>
			<img src="<%=System.Web.Configuration.WebConfigurationManager.AppSettings["ImagePath"] %>images/i45_houston_dallas/i45_n_of_corsicana_3_2004-11-28_770.jpg">
